{"tid":1163702,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(DC大作) Keanu 表示自己最想再一次扮演角色就是Constantine","createTime":"2019-05-20T15:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T06:41:15.000Z","uid":98659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0d7a16ecddf120ebbdc151dcc08e2c1ccdc6f4","tid":1163702,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:06:42.000Z","msg":"說到基努李維（Keanu Reeves）的代表作，除了九零年代的《駭客任務》（The Matrix）三部曲，或是近期上映的《捍衛任務》（John Wick）系列，相信忠實影迷一定還記得 2005 年上映的《康斯坦汀：驅魔神探》（Constantine）吧！<br />\n<br />\n這部改編自 DC 漫畫的電影作品，在角色個性以及劇情上都做了不少的修改，雖然票房不如《駭客任務》那麼轟動，但也算是賣得不錯，而且當年令人耳目一新的黑色幽默劇情設定、美術風格等等，都讓這部片累積了不少忠實粉絲，至今已經過了 14 年卻一直未有續集，是不少影迷心中的萬年懸念之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=955&amp;v=JExYdAXEWTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D955%26v%3DJExYdAXEWTs&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=f2f9de00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=955&amp;v=JExYdAXEWTs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於遲遲未有續集的原因是什麼呢？普遍的理由被認為是主角基努李維不想演，不過最近他在宣傳新片《捍衛任務 3：全面開戰》時，被問到最想回歸的電影角色是什麼，這位大明星卻清楚的表示自己最想再一次扮演的角色就是「約翰・康斯坦汀」！<br />\n<br />\n而且基努李維還提到，最主要的原因在於，自己非常喜歡《康斯坦汀：驅魔神探》這部片的世界觀。<br />\n<br />\n等待了十四年的電影續集，如今不少老影迷可能早就不期不待了。但如果是由基努李維這位大明星主動表示想演出，再加上近來 DC 的策略從發展「DC 宇宙」改為專心塑造每個個性角色的故事，而康斯坦汀又恰好是觀眾們已經有點熟悉的角色，相信更有深度挖掘的亮點，說不定期待已久的影迷們，真的有希望在這股超級英雄熱中實現這個不可能的任務呢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.juksy.com/archives/89261?atl=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.juksy.com%2Farchives%2F89261%3Fatl%3D1&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=ac4dfbca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.juksy.com/archives/89261?atl=1</a>"},{"pid":"4f0af39510904e76068438a0d7482a42aa21ed4c","tid":1163702,"uid":246165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"拍多集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba7507c460ae02e507e79579f033f3b6cc459bd","tid":1163702,"uid":98659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"Dc ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 古一番黎dc大家庭"},{"pid":"9bedd3e02bb7cc3177d2349e1fabcbbfff24f427","tid":1163702,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"真心好鐘意，希望拍多 d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0730c29168fe472d0b62d4018abfd3bd343290","tid":1163702,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:01:39.000Z","msg":"dc又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28415e6bb76229a29b20e800cd40b7a989aacda4","tid":1163702,"uid":81914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"屌 快d拍  以前係有線睇 已經覺得好撚正  一開波女仔比鬼上身個段到依家都重好記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}